Projects.Title: Save My Data
Projects.ShortDescription: A fast easy to integrate API for dumping unstructured data
Projects.FullDescription:
Working with databases is not always a pleasant experience to do especially if we need to save small data on the go.
So I created a service tool that makes this process easy and fast for both developers and non-developing experienced people that lets users save, edit, read and export there data in different file formats such as excel, csv and more.
